				<outline text="&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.theregister.co.uk/content/4/21347.html&quot;&gt;Linus Torvalds&lt;/a&gt;. &quot;If Microsoft is going to tax everyone on the Internet, don't think the governments will watch their monopoly on tax collection go by.&quot;"/>
