				<outline text="Tonight's Scripting News dinner is at Vincent's, 8PM. 119 Mott St, at Hester St (212-226-8133). &quot;Little Italy restaurant serving fresh, cheap and spicy seafood dishes – clams, mussels and squid.&quot; RSVP &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.userland.com/surveys/run/dave@userland.com/dinnerInNyOnMonday&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;." type="link" url="http://www.userland.com/surveys/run/dave@userland.com/dinnerInNyOnMonday"/>
