				<outline text="One of the latest home page-flips in recent memory. Not much to say. Spent the day with NY family members and my Jamaican uncle. Toured various old neighborhoods, went bowling, spoke Italian, ate deli food, had a great time. Today the computer industry can take care of itself. And my email is working again. "/>
