				<outline text="&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.edge.org/digerati/brockman/&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.scripting.com/images/brockmanThumbAndSignatureHa.gif&quot; height=&quot;41&quot; width=&quot;40&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; hspace=&quot;10&quot; vspace=&quot;10&quot; align=&quot;right&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Last night I talked with NY book agent and digerati salon-man &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.edge.org/digerati/brockman/&quot;&gt;John Brockman&lt;/a&gt;. He asked if I'd heard from Linda Stone lately. While I was getting ready to say no, my emailer checked in with the server and downloaded a message from.. &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.girlgeeks.com/innergeek/inspiringwomen/stone.html&quot;&gt;Linda Stone&lt;/a&gt;. I asked if she'd been channeling lately. She said she had but it wasn't doing much good. (Stone is Microsoft's exec in charge of making everyone outside MS love MS.)"/>
